reviewText: A totally compelling psychological thriller. The girl is completely hot, not sure where you'd find actual hookers of this caliber! By the end of the movie though, you might not want to (not because she's not hot, because she is. Totally).
Ready to have your world rocked? Mine definitely got shaken. This is some pretty dark and twisted stuff. Right up my alley!
I dig movies like this. Sex and violent mayhem all wrapped up in a cool indie burrito. This one is a standout.
